parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Headlight Failure Due to Moisture Ingress
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headlights can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at night. The dimming of headlights can also cause discomfort to oncoming traffic, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: making it difficult to see the road at night
water droplets or fogging inside the headlight housing
low beam headlights are very dim
high beam headlights are needed to compensate for low beam dimness.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear suspension toe link can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, and potentially resulting in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle may sway or vibrate while driving
the traction control warning light may illuminate
the vehicle may pull to one side
and the rear tires may wear down prematurely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear axle can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, and potentially resulting in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The "Service Rear Axle" message may display on the instrument panel
the vehicle may vibrate or shake while driving
and the rear tires may wear down prematurely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of parts for recall repairs can cause delays and inconvenience to vehicle owners, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Vehicle owners may experience delays or unavailability of parts for recall repairs
leading to extended periods of time without a safe and reliable vehicle.
